/**
 * "Kitchen Order App" rename — applies the order-accepting app's new name
 * across all 38 locale message files.
 *
 *  - VERBATIM_PATHS  → the fixed English brand "Kitchen Order App" in EVERY
 *                      locale (Luigi: one name everywhere, like GrowthNet).
 *  - PROSE (s1..s9)  → sentences where the term is embedded; re-translated per
 *                      locale with "Kitchen Order App" kept in English.
 *
 *  Leaves the coming-soon "Kitchen Display System (KDS)" strings untouched
 *  (admin.kdsPage.*, admin.sidebar.kitchenDisplay → the KDS nav item).
 *
 *  Array-index segments (freeIncludes.3, faq.items.6.a) are handled safely —
 *  unlike i18n-merge-data's setDeep, which would clobber the array.
 *
 *    npx tsx scripts/apply-kitchen-order-app-rename.ts
 */
